# ==========================================================================
# postbird .gitignore
# The working tree carries a lot of LOCAL reference material that must NOT be
# published: the maintainer's real inbox screenshots (privacy), Postbox's
# proprietary theme (copyright), the multi-thousand-file Betterbird omni.ja
# extraction (bloat + third-party MPL), and other people's userChrome projects.
# We publish only the theme itself + docs + scripts. See refs/README.md for how
# to repopulate refs/ locally.
# ==========================================================================

# --- refs/: all local reference material, EXCEPT the version pin + its readme.
refs/*
!refs/betterbird-version.txt
!refs/README.md

# --- Local, machine-specific, or regenerable ---
.codegraph/

# --- AI-assistant assets: kept LOCAL (agents still use them), not published ---
.claude/
.gemini/
.mcp.json
CLAUDE.md
claude.md
GEMINI.md
AGENTS.md

# --- OS / editor noise ---
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.swp
